TECHNICAL ANALYSIS
How Ghost Site Redirection Works:
Method 1: DNS Hijacking

Francesco's DNS requests intercepted
Redirected to fake IP address hosting mirror site
Mirror site designed to look identical to real platform
All traffic logged before selectively displaying content
Method 2: Browser/System Compromise

Malware on Francesco's device
Intercepts all web traffic at system level
Redirects specific URLs to surveillance-controlled servers
Allows monitoring of all activity
Method 3: ISP/Network Level Interception

Internet Service Provider cooperation (voluntary or compelled)
Traffic redirected at network infrastructure level
Government has access to backbone routing
Can target specific users without device compromise
Method 4: Certificate Spoofing

Fake SSL/TLS certificates presented
Browser shows "secure connection" but it's to surveillance server
Requires certificate authority compromise or government certificate
